55:32.200 --> 55:34.399
Justin! Justin!

55:35.320 --> 55:37.919
Wait a minute! Wait...

55:39.880 --> 55:44.039
Hey? No! Don't you...
Don't you... Hey!

55:44.480 --> 55:45.679
Get up!

55:47.120 --> 55:48.319
Justin!

55:50.800 --> 55:52.439
No, get up!

56:02.520 --> 56:03.519
Get up!

56:11.240 --> 56:13.319
Come on, mate, get up! Get up!

